data.description: Price Improvement!! Beautiful, Updated, Move in Ready Home in established quiet neighborhood! Beautiful curb appeal and a cute covered porch greets you as you walk up to this home! The front door is a beautiful wood carved door and is one of a kind! This home is light and bright with updated paint colors throughout! There are 2 living areas and 2 dining areas in this well appointed floor plan! The Kitchen is open to the family room with a beautiful fireplace a great space for gatherings with family and friends! Home has two Water Heaters and a New Oven with built in air fryer!  Garage is oversized and has amazing storage! The large back yard with trees, above ground pool, covered deck and storage is the perfect place or entertaining or just relaxing! Don't miss out on this home! You will love the upgrades that have been made while keeping the character in this home!
